WEBVTT

00:16.030 --> 00:18.290
It's the gun from the 8.17 Case, isn't it?

00:18.560 --> 00:20.360
Is Zhou Jin working on this case?

00:21.010 --> 00:23.870
She's now responsible for
identifying the victim.

00:26.730 --> 00:28.410
Are you scared,

00:29.040 --> 00:30.290
Officer Jiang?

02:04.660 --> 02:10.620
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:10.940 --> 02:13.420
[Episode 4]

02:14.470 --> 02:15.380
I can see that.

02:17.079 --> 02:18.810
I know what you're trying to do.

02:19.460 --> 02:20.020
Really,

02:20.290 --> 02:21.210
we were so close.

02:21.210 --> 02:22.270
Just a little more,

02:23.090 --> 02:24.930
and his mental defenses
would have been broken.

02:24.930 --> 02:26.050
Think about it.

02:26.980 --> 02:28.310
Someone who can get a gun

02:28.780 --> 02:30.180
can't be a nobody, right?

02:32.880 --> 02:35.140
Handling a case is never smooth sailing.

02:35.460 --> 02:36.860
It's not your first time.

02:37.730 --> 02:38.410
Alright.

02:42.550 --> 02:44.550
Are you planning to cry here?

02:47.670 --> 02:48.670
Oh my.

02:50.340 --> 02:51.570
That's a huge bump.

02:53.329 --> 02:55.460
Go to the infirmary and get it checked.

02:55.920 --> 02:57.200
Let me try one more time, please.

02:57.200 --> 02:58.110
Just one more time.

02:58.110 --> 02:58.910
Alright.

03:00.370 --> 03:01.530
Haste makes waste.

03:01.620 --> 03:02.710
It's such a pity!

03:02.740 --> 03:03.300
Zhou Jin.

03:06.710 --> 03:08.950
Don't get stuck in the 8·17 Case.

03:09.500 --> 03:11.010
I understand how you feel.

03:11.510 --> 03:13.190
We've tried your plan.

03:13.220 --> 03:14.100
Reality proves

03:15.050 --> 03:15.980
that this method

03:16.300 --> 03:17.140
doesn't work.

03:18.190 --> 03:18.720
Alright.

03:21.579 --> 03:23.579
Don't forget to go to the infirmary.

03:43.000 --> 03:44.360
Pursuing like this is too dangerous.

03:44.360 --> 03:45.329
We can easily crash.

03:45.329 --> 03:48.260
Let's set up a roadblock at the exit
to intercept him.

04:02.120 --> 04:03.090
Let's go.

04:07.750 --> 04:09.220
You drove out of town
as soon as you got in the car.

04:09.220 --> 04:10.620
What are you trying to do?

04:10.780 --> 04:11.760
He's operating without a license.

04:11.760 --> 04:12.560
He felt guilty

04:12.660 --> 04:14.380
and thought you were here
to catch illegal cabs.

04:14.380 --> 04:15.910
We just want to ask a few questions.

04:15.910 --> 04:17.200
You've delayed us for so long.

04:17.200 --> 04:17.980
Sorry, sorry.

04:17.980 --> 04:18.860
I didn't know.

04:18.890 --> 04:20.089
I seriously suspect

04:20.110 --> 04:21.190
you're involved in other cases.

04:21.190 --> 04:22.070
No, no.

04:22.210 --> 04:24.200
Officer, please don't joke like that.

04:24.200 --> 04:25.200
Let me remind you.

04:26.260 --> 04:27.610
On the night of July 23rd,

04:27.610 --> 04:29.050
did you get a ride request

04:29.310 --> 04:31.330
to go to the Tonghe riverside
in the middle of the night?

04:31.330 --> 04:32.940
The night of July 23rd?

04:33.990 --> 04:34.990
Think carefully.

04:35.940 --> 04:38.540
To the Tonghe riverside
in the middle of the night?

04:38.540 --> 04:39.180
Yes.

04:39.520 --> 04:40.370
There was such a person.

04:40.370 --> 04:41.010
And then?

04:41.210 --> 04:43.020
And then I went at the agreed time

04:43.040 --> 04:45.070
and drove to the Tonghe riverside
to pick them up.

04:45.070 --> 04:46.000
Did you get them?

04:46.170 --> 04:46.780
No.

04:46.800 --> 04:48.940
I only saw the person who booked the ride.

04:48.940 --> 04:50.570
The person who booked the ride?

04:50.570 --> 04:52.190
The one who booked wasn't the passenger?

04:52.190 --> 04:52.659
Right.

04:52.970 --> 04:53.680
Was it a man?

04:54.020 --> 04:54.420
Right.

04:58.040 --> 04:58.730
Is this him?

05:00.080 --> 05:00.730
No.

05:00.980 --> 05:01.790
Look closely.

05:02.600 --> 05:03.730
It's really not him.

05:04.830 --> 05:05.500
I'm not trying to criticize you,

05:05.500 --> 05:07.060
but can you not answer only when asked?

05:07.060 --> 05:07.860
Say a bit more.

05:08.900 --> 05:09.940
I'm a bit nervous.

05:10.560 --> 05:11.440
That night,

05:11.860 --> 05:13.010
I drove to the Tonghe riverside.

05:13.010 --> 05:13.970
I kept waiting,

05:14.450 --> 05:15.430
but no one showed up,

05:15.430 --> 05:17.610
so I called the person who booked the car.

05:17.610 --> 05:18.900
He was nearby.

05:19.420 --> 05:21.780
When he came over,
he even took the suitcase out of the car.

05:21.780 --> 05:23.610
He told me his sister
wasn't leaving anymore.

05:23.610 --> 05:25.340
Anyway, he looked quite young.

05:25.660 --> 05:27.590
It wasn't the person in your photo.

05:27.610 --> 05:29.250
If I let you see this person again,

05:29.250 --> 05:30.170
could you recognize him?

05:30.170 --> 05:30.850
Yes.

05:31.250 --> 05:32.780
That guy had bleached hair,

05:33.050 --> 05:34.510
so he's easy to recognize.

05:50.340 --> 05:50.930
Bleach,

05:51.460 --> 05:52.590
you're lucky today.

05:53.440 --> 05:54.780
You've met a good person.

05:54.780 --> 05:56.460
Since this lady is so curious,

05:56.730 --> 05:59.130
you better answer her questions properly.

06:02.370 --> 06:03.660
It seems to be...

06:03.760 --> 06:04.510
Number three.

06:04.510 --> 06:05.690
What do you mean "seems"?

06:05.690 --> 06:06.490
Look closely.

06:09.250 --> 06:10.490
Yes, that's right.

06:11.000 --> 06:11.660
That's him.

06:12.660 --> 06:13.460
Number three?

06:13.530 --> 06:14.290
Yes.

06:16.510 --> 06:18.220
Sir, your task is done.

06:18.250 --> 06:19.060
Come with me.

06:19.900 --> 06:20.610
Goodbye.

06:28.220 --> 06:28.820
Zhao Ping.

06:30.150 --> 06:32.080
Come interrogate this guy with me.

06:32.190 --> 06:32.680
Yes.

06:32.710 --> 06:33.350
Sir.

06:35.300 --> 06:37.700
Haven't you embarrassed yourself enough?

06:38.610 --> 06:39.140
Let's go.

06:51.170 --> 06:52.860
Mr. Wan, Liang, I'm heading out.

06:52.860 --> 06:53.460
Okay.

06:54.420 --> 06:55.130
Want some?

06:55.370 --> 06:56.050
I can't eat.

06:56.580 --> 06:57.780
Is it from Chuanwang?

06:57.930 --> 06:59.290
Once I deliver the baby, I'm going to eat

06:59.290 --> 07:00.490
every dish at Chuanwang

07:00.490 --> 07:01.980
and all the junk food.

07:02.000 --> 07:03.460
Just hold out a bit longer.

07:03.730 --> 07:04.460
Smells so good.

07:04.460 --> 07:06.520
Let me smell it to satisfy my craving.

07:10.420 --> 07:11.050
Zhou,

07:11.280 --> 07:13.210
if you're sleepy, go get some rest.

07:13.860 --> 07:14.930
I'm not sleepy.

07:15.780 --> 07:16.900
What do you mean you're not sleepy?

07:16.900 --> 07:18.230
Why are you so stubborn?

07:18.250 --> 07:19.690
Don't complain about my nagging.

07:19.690 --> 07:21.070
When I first joined the force,

07:21.070 --> 07:22.470
I stayed up late too much,

07:22.490 --> 07:23.490
and as a result...

07:24.810 --> 07:25.940
I picked up smoking.

07:26.220 --> 07:28.170
Now I can't quit even if I want to.

07:28.470 --> 07:29.670
You just got married.

07:29.780 --> 07:31.130
What if you want a child,

07:31.130 --> 07:32.600
but your body can't handle it?

07:32.600 --> 07:33.810
Does what I'm saying make sense?

07:33.810 --> 07:34.540
Does it?

07:34.710 --> 07:35.800
If you won't think of yourself,

07:35.800 --> 07:36.860
think of your future child,

07:36.860 --> 07:37.810
okay?

07:37.860 --> 07:38.659
Professor Jiang,

07:38.659 --> 07:39.790
you're here so late.

07:45.100 --> 07:45.760
Cigarettes

07:46.210 --> 07:47.010
cause cancer.

07:47.730 --> 07:49.190
You must never touch them.

07:50.020 --> 07:51.420
Professor Jiang is here.

07:51.600 --> 07:53.060
Everyone, look after him.

07:53.370 --> 07:54.430
I'm going to smoke.

08:02.170 --> 08:03.170
Where's Zhou Jin?

08:03.550 --> 08:04.140
Zhou,

08:04.860 --> 08:06.060
your husband is here.

08:08.860 --> 08:09.790
Why are you here?

08:10.800 --> 08:12.070
So sweet,

08:12.100 --> 08:14.500
bringing a love-filled meal late at night.

08:22.690 --> 08:23.460
We can eat it.

08:23.610 --> 08:24.940
Can't let it go to waste.

08:29.020 --> 08:30.020
Have some with us.

08:30.020 --> 08:30.610
No need.

08:30.970 --> 08:32.970
Watching you two is filling enough.

08:39.809 --> 08:40.320
Did you

08:40.820 --> 08:42.020
come here specially?

08:42.980 --> 08:44.100
I cooked too much.

08:46.610 --> 08:47.410
Are you...

08:49.830 --> 08:52.080
The AC is too high here.

08:52.220 --> 08:53.620
It's making my head hurt.

08:53.700 --> 08:54.360
A headache?

09:06.220 --> 09:07.980
Let's go to the dorm.

09:19.010 --> 09:19.460
Sis,

09:19.700 --> 09:21.300
just watching is bad for you.

09:22.050 --> 09:23.250
Eat the food.

09:25.490 --> 09:26.950
Actually, there's no need

09:27.060 --> 09:27.890
to cook for me.

09:27.890 --> 09:29.090
I'm not a picky eater.

09:29.640 --> 09:30.520
I eat anything.

09:32.280 --> 09:33.210
It's no trouble.

09:45.250 --> 09:46.530
That's my brother.

09:49.530 --> 09:50.180
I know.

09:50.890 --> 09:52.550
How come you know everything?

09:53.530 --> 09:55.220
When you lived in Zhizi Alley,

09:55.250 --> 09:56.410
you barely went out,

09:57.650 --> 09:59.450
but you seemed to know everyone.

09:59.580 --> 10:00.840
You have great memory.

10:14.530 --> 10:15.700
Now you can tell me

10:16.300 --> 10:17.900
why you're like this, right?

10:19.980 --> 10:20.860
This dish

10:21.720 --> 10:22.580
is really good.

10:23.100 --> 10:25.230
I haven't tried this one. Let me try it.

10:28.170 --> 10:29.500
It has kiwi in it, right?

10:30.150 --> 10:30.680
Zhou Jin,

10:31.430 --> 10:32.890
don't change the subject.

10:34.850 --> 10:35.730
Migraine.

10:39.410 --> 10:40.100
Don't move.

10:53.730 --> 10:55.650
I'm fine. It's nothing.

10:58.050 --> 10:58.720
Who did it?

11:00.300 --> 11:01.560
Lai San bumped into me.

11:01.860 --> 11:03.120
You interrogated him?

11:03.240 --> 11:04.550
I tried to provoke him.

11:05.930 --> 11:06.600
Zhou Jin.

11:07.650 --> 11:09.640
You clearly haven't
been on the front lines, have you?

11:09.640 --> 11:10.930
Anyone who has

11:10.950 --> 11:12.330
knows that this is a minor injury.

11:12.330 --> 11:14.020
It's no big deal, really.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.040
I clearly told you

11:16.340 --> 11:17.800
to inform Chief Tan first.

11:18.240 --> 11:19.840
I was worried this would happen.

11:19.840 --> 11:20.970
I don't understand.

11:21.310 --> 11:22.970
Yes, I was a little impulsive.

11:23.340 --> 11:24.980
I tried to provoke Lai San.

11:25.020 --> 11:27.100
But isn't luring him
to admit to his crime

11:27.100 --> 11:29.700
a perfectly normal
interrogation technique?

11:29.730 --> 11:31.410
But you knew full well this method

11:31.410 --> 11:32.740
would put you in danger.

11:32.890 --> 11:34.680
Is there any investigation
that isn't dangerous?

11:34.680 --> 11:35.860
You are a psychology expert.

11:35.860 --> 11:37.060
You should know better than me

11:37.060 --> 11:38.290
that in this situation,

11:38.290 --> 11:40.100
it's more appropriate for a woman to go.

11:40.100 --> 11:41.490
Plus, we have history.

11:41.490 --> 11:43.580
There is no one on the whole squad

11:43.580 --> 11:44.580
more suitable for this.

11:44.580 --> 11:45.910
And what was the result?

11:45.950 --> 11:47.260
That result is you got hurt,

11:47.260 --> 11:48.220
and he didn't confess.

11:48.220 --> 11:49.460
But I tried.

11:49.490 --> 11:50.490
I have no regrets.

11:56.130 --> 11:56.770
I'm sorry.

11:57.900 --> 11:59.140
I need to cool down.

12:35.460 --> 12:35.980
No!

12:36.180 --> 12:37.010
Nobody move!

12:37.010 --> 12:38.010
Don't kill me!

12:38.380 --> 12:39.100
No!

12:40.020 --> 12:40.740
No!

12:43.580 --> 12:44.680
Don't kill me!

12:50.460 --> 12:52.150
Are you scared yet,

12:52.910 --> 12:54.150
Officer Jiang?

13:28.900 --> 13:29.610
I'm sorry.

13:31.490 --> 13:33.460
I had a bad attitude just now.

13:34.840 --> 13:36.700
I didn't consider your feelings.

13:37.490 --> 13:38.410
Actually,

13:40.490 --> 13:42.150
you're just worried about me.

14:03.530 --> 14:04.180
Hansheng,

14:05.700 --> 14:07.820
investigations and interrogations

14:07.820 --> 14:10.280
are both duties
of a criminal investigator.

14:10.710 --> 14:13.510
Whether I can get something out of him
is one thing.

14:13.820 --> 14:16.500
Whether I go interrogate him is another.

14:17.890 --> 14:19.010
I know today,

14:19.220 --> 14:20.490
he didn't admit it,

14:21.460 --> 14:22.790
but during the process,

14:23.010 --> 14:24.300
for a brief moment,

14:25.450 --> 14:26.880
he almost gave in.

14:27.250 --> 14:28.940
Really, he was just one step away

14:28.940 --> 14:30.100
from confessing.

14:45.010 --> 14:46.940
I have to get used to facing danger.

14:49.920 --> 14:52.580
And you have to get used to
facing this side of me.

14:53.870 --> 14:55.730
Lai San is just a marginal figure.

14:56.680 --> 14:57.490
In the future,

14:58.180 --> 14:59.720
there might be more dangerous things

14:59.720 --> 15:00.520
I need to face.

15:01.870 --> 15:02.710
I know.

15:04.170 --> 15:05.860
I'm just a rookie on this team.

15:06.750 --> 15:07.950
There are many people

15:08.260 --> 15:09.280
who are more experienced,

15:09.280 --> 15:10.240
more capable,

15:10.270 --> 15:11.400
and smarter than me.

15:12.970 --> 15:14.130
But the team is still willing

15:14.130 --> 15:16.390
to give me such trust and opportunities.

15:16.970 --> 15:18.570
I don't want to let them down.

15:20.040 --> 15:21.500
Even if I must risk my life,

15:22.090 --> 15:23.130
I won't back down.

15:24.450 --> 15:26.310
This is not just for the 8.17 Case,

15:26.490 --> 15:28.090
nor is it just for my brother.

15:29.080 --> 15:30.200
Do you understand?

15:38.610 --> 15:39.400
Hansheng,

15:40.520 --> 15:41.580
you're trembling.

15:42.920 --> 15:43.680
I'm sorry.

15:45.370 --> 15:46.830
I raised my voice just now.

15:49.520 --> 15:50.330
Today

15:51.760 --> 15:53.690
was the first time you yelled at me.

16:12.480 --> 16:14.000
As expected of newlyweds,

16:14.850 --> 16:17.190
sticking to each other like glue.

16:23.200 --> 16:24.210
Done interrogating?

16:24.210 --> 16:24.880
Done.

16:25.440 --> 16:28.240
Huang Song is much easier to deal with
than Lai San.

16:30.080 --> 16:31.890
His real name is Huang Song.

16:32.020 --> 16:33.480
He dropped out of Haizhou Vocational
and Technical College

16:33.480 --> 16:35.030
after less than a year.

16:35.270 --> 16:36.290
He's from a single-parent family,

16:36.290 --> 16:37.820
raised by his mother alone.

16:38.010 --> 16:39.080
During his school years,

16:39.080 --> 16:39.930
he didn't get along well

16:39.930 --> 16:41.680
with his teachers or classmates.

16:41.680 --> 16:43.080
His grades were also poor.

16:43.080 --> 16:44.490
Probably because of this,

16:44.490 --> 16:46.600
he hated staying at school more and more,

16:46.600 --> 16:47.930
and often skipped class

16:47.930 --> 16:49.530
to hang out with young thugs.

16:49.960 --> 16:51.490
Later, he met Lai Zhengtian

16:51.770 --> 16:53.930
and started introducing young girls
to the nightclub.

16:53.930 --> 16:54.680
Over time,

16:54.900 --> 16:56.960
Lai Zhengtian took him in as a lackey.

16:57.500 --> 17:02.560
[2015]

17:10.349 --> 17:11.810
Hey, hottie, have a drink.

17:22.290 --> 17:23.000
Lai!

17:27.599 --> 17:28.600
Your commission.

17:30.810 --> 17:32.400
This is too much, Lai.

17:32.670 --> 17:34.110
This money is nothing.

17:34.170 --> 17:36.100
Today's drinks cost over 100,000.

17:36.460 --> 17:37.070
Come!

17:39.800 --> 17:40.480
Here's to you!

17:40.480 --> 17:41.930
Lai, I'll drink to yoU!

17:44.720 --> 17:45.280
Bro,

17:46.100 --> 17:47.370
you know what's the most important thing

17:47.370 --> 17:48.830
for a man in this business?

17:50.680 --> 17:51.410
I don't know.

17:52.280 --> 17:53.170
It's...

17:54.900 --> 17:55.940
Face!

17:59.450 --> 18:00.130
Got it?

18:00.520 --> 18:01.440
Got it, bro.

18:01.750 --> 18:03.860
From now on, you just stick with me.

18:04.030 --> 18:05.660
This world will be ours!

18:07.930 --> 18:08.610
Lai,

18:09.350 --> 18:10.670
let me toast you.

18:11.610 --> 18:12.090
Come on.

18:12.810 --> 18:14.080
I have high hopes for you.

18:14.080 --> 18:14.940
Thank you, Lai.

18:18.110 --> 18:20.550
What was the relationship
between Meng Ling and Lai Zhengtian?

18:20.550 --> 18:22.420
Meng Ling was one of Lai's girls.

18:23.230 --> 18:25.490
She was the most popular with the guests,

18:26.050 --> 18:27.310
but she wasn't honest.

18:28.200 --> 18:29.680
She had dirt on Lai.

18:30.610 --> 18:31.410
Lai said

18:31.930 --> 18:33.060
she was a hot potato.

18:34.150 --> 18:35.950
She needed to be dealt with ASAP.

18:37.130 --> 18:37.930
What dirt?

18:39.460 --> 18:40.190
I don't know.

18:40.620 --> 18:43.180
Did "dealing with her ASAP"
mean killing Meng Ling?

18:43.180 --> 18:45.230
He didn't want to kill her originally

18:45.230 --> 18:45.900
because...

18:47.070 --> 18:48.330
Jiang Cheng came back.

18:48.870 --> 18:50.070
Lai was scared of him.

18:50.810 --> 18:51.810
He didn't dare to.

18:52.210 --> 18:52.940
Jiang Cheng?

18:53.540 --> 18:54.600
Which Jiang Cheng?

18:55.260 --> 18:56.720
The one from Phoenix Fire?

18:56.930 --> 18:57.480
Yes, him.

18:58.490 --> 19:00.820
What does this
have to do with Jiang Cheng?

19:02.910 --> 19:04.870
Jiang Cheng is a very capable guy.

19:06.150 --> 19:08.340
Actually, I only heard about it.

19:09.000 --> 19:10.760
Boss He likes smart

19:10.780 --> 19:12.040
and efficient people.

19:12.630 --> 19:13.980
Boss He thought highly of Jiang Cheng

19:13.980 --> 19:15.850
as soon as he joined the company.

19:16.780 --> 19:19.040
He took Jiang Cheng with him everywhere.

19:19.520 --> 19:21.110
But Jiang Cheng and Lai didn't get along

19:21.110 --> 19:21.970
from the start.

19:22.750 --> 19:25.150
They even fought a few times
over business.

19:25.480 --> 19:26.610
Boss He saw that the two of them

19:26.610 --> 19:28.140
really couldn't get along.

19:29.240 --> 19:29.810
So,

19:29.810 --> 19:33.010
he transferred Jiang Cheng
to a branch office out of town.

19:33.350 --> 19:34.510
Actually, Lai knew

19:35.350 --> 19:37.280
Boss He was reluctant to let him go.

19:38.110 --> 19:40.110
It's just because Lai is his cousin.

19:40.650 --> 19:41.650
Family, you know.

19:41.960 --> 19:42.910
It's different.

19:43.280 --> 19:44.890
Then why did Jiang Cheng come back?

19:44.890 --> 19:46.490
Because he signed a big order

19:47.270 --> 19:48.870
and became a Hengyun's hero,

19:49.500 --> 19:51.330
so he was transferred back.

19:51.830 --> 19:54.430
This Lai San
doesn't dare to touch Jiang Cheng?

19:55.470 --> 19:57.090
Lai's been having bad luck.

19:58.140 --> 19:59.200
He was afraid
that after Jiang Cheng's return,

19:59.200 --> 20:01.460
he wouldn't be able to keep his position,

20:01.580 --> 20:04.510
so he hasn't dared to
make a single mistake recently.

20:05.240 --> 20:07.030
Would touching Meng Ling
be considered a mistake?

20:07.030 --> 20:08.270
How could it not be?

20:09.130 --> 20:10.930
Meng Ling used to be with Jiang Cheng.

20:10.930 --> 20:12.250
If Lai really touched her,

20:12.250 --> 20:14.160
Jiang Cheng would end him.

20:14.250 --> 20:14.780
Explain.

20:15.050 --> 20:15.910
She was with Jiang Cheng.

20:15.910 --> 20:16.590
In what way?

20:17.630 --> 20:19.150
Just... that kind of way.

20:21.200 --> 20:21.800
As lovers.

20:23.480 --> 20:24.000
Go on.

20:24.840 --> 20:25.550
Lai said

20:26.510 --> 20:28.420
Jiang Cheng used to be a cop.

20:29.740 --> 20:31.560
If Jiang Cheng
really wanted to mess with him,

20:31.560 --> 20:32.900
he might not be able to handle it.

20:32.900 --> 20:35.100
You all know Jiang Cheng used to be a cop?

20:36.760 --> 20:37.280
Yes.

20:38.740 --> 20:41.600
I heard he was dismissed
for violating discipline.

20:42.080 --> 20:43.720
Later he followed Boss He...

20:46.320 --> 20:47.480
and went into business.

20:47.480 --> 20:48.340
What business?

20:48.680 --> 20:50.480
Making a gangster sound so nice.

20:50.760 --> 20:51.520
A cop?

20:51.840 --> 20:53.320
Don't dirty our name.

20:58.810 --> 20:59.560
Go on.

21:02.670 --> 21:04.430
Lai was afraid of Jiang Cheng,

21:05.310 --> 21:07.040
so he promised to give Meng Ling

21:07.460 --> 21:08.810
a sum of money

21:09.310 --> 21:12.040
as compensation for her hard work
over the years.

21:12.220 --> 21:13.750
Then he asked me to find a car

21:13.950 --> 21:15.750
and send her back to her hometown

21:16.210 --> 21:17.740
to settle the matter early.

21:18.480 --> 21:19.940
You call shooting someone

21:19.940 --> 21:21.350
"settling the matter"?

21:23.930 --> 21:26.660
That's because she was stupid
and had a big mouth!

21:27.040 --> 21:27.610
Lai just

21:27.610 --> 21:29.280
insulted Jiang Cheng a little.

21:29.280 --> 21:30.960
Usually, no matter how Lai punished her,

21:30.960 --> 21:32.200
she wouldn't make a sound.

21:32.200 --> 21:34.080
But he mentioned Jiang Cheng
and she went crazy!

21:34.080 --> 21:35.740
Why did she favor Jiang Cheng?

21:37.580 --> 21:39.380
That's why I say she's stupid.

21:43.520 --> 21:45.020
I want to eat steak today.

21:45.560 --> 21:46.100
How about it?

21:46.100 --> 21:47.300
That place is not bad.

21:56.060 --> 21:56.660
Meng Ling,

21:56.740 --> 21:58.600
I have something to do. I gotta go.

22:01.040 --> 22:02.170
Not staying to chat?

22:06.720 --> 22:07.850
Not bad, Meng.

22:08.620 --> 22:09.950
You're almost becoming

22:10.070 --> 22:11.510
the top prostitute.

22:12.740 --> 22:13.870
Where are you going?

22:14.360 --> 22:15.620
You still want to shop?

22:15.630 --> 22:17.350
You want to dirty up this mall?

22:19.350 --> 22:21.130
Are you something clean yourself?

22:21.130 --> 22:22.200
Talking back?

22:28.070 --> 22:30.470
Jiang Cheng, are you crazy?
You dare hit me?

22:31.020 --> 22:32.880
What does this have to do with you?

22:33.130 --> 22:34.460
Who do you think you are?

22:34.960 --> 22:36.720
I'm her man, okay?

22:40.380 --> 22:42.790
She believed whatever others said.

22:44.410 --> 22:46.270
It was like that with Jiang Cheng,

22:46.650 --> 22:48.250
and it was like that with Lai.

22:49.130 --> 22:51.130
She believed whatever others said.

22:52.580 --> 22:54.310
Tell me how Lai San tricked her.

22:55.810 --> 22:57.810
Letting her go back to her hometown.

22:58.350 --> 22:59.610
Wasn't that just a lie?

23:00.450 --> 23:00.970
Sister,

23:02.120 --> 23:06.280
[July 23 22:28]

23:02.350 --> 23:03.740
why aren't you at home?

23:05.550 --> 23:06.070
I'm not.

23:07.160 --> 23:08.750
The driver is here.

23:09.070 --> 23:10.640
How about I put your suitcase

23:10.640 --> 23:11.570
in the car first?

23:11.570 --> 23:13.300
Is Lai San really letting me go?

23:13.370 --> 23:13.890
Really.

23:14.480 --> 23:15.520
But Lai said

23:15.520 --> 23:17.650
you must bring what he wants

23:17.650 --> 23:20.050
and then we'll go to
Tonghe to meet with him.

23:20.750 --> 23:21.970
Once he gets the stuff,

23:21.970 --> 23:23.370
he should let you go home.

23:23.680 --> 23:25.340
He also asked me to tell you...

23:26.110 --> 23:27.270
Don't play tricks.

23:28.570 --> 23:30.300
Lai San has moments of fear too?

23:32.260 --> 23:32.790
Sister,

23:33.550 --> 23:35.920
what dirt do you have on Lai?

23:38.640 --> 23:40.170
It's better you don't know.

23:43.640 --> 23:46.590
Actually, I'd really hate
to part with you.

23:46.670 --> 23:47.190
Really.

23:47.550 --> 23:48.280
To be honest,

23:48.660 --> 23:49.800
among all these people,

23:49.800 --> 23:52.460
you are the second person
to truly care about me.

23:52.480 --> 23:53.830
You call me your sister.

23:54.150 --> 23:56.010
It's only right I take care of you.

23:56.450 --> 23:57.480
I'm leaving soon.

23:57.800 --> 24:00.130
Before I go, let me remind you
of one thing.

24:00.870 --> 24:04.190
Go to school. Study hard.

24:04.220 --> 24:06.590
Stop hanging out with Lai.

24:06.930 --> 24:08.930
I've heard this so many times.

24:08.950 --> 24:10.260
Not this.

24:11.050 --> 24:11.940
Then what?

24:13.350 --> 24:14.480
Be nicer to your mom.

24:15.540 --> 24:16.940
If my mom were still alive

24:18.160 --> 24:20.090
and saw me being bullied like this,

24:20.180 --> 24:21.640
she would be heartbroken.

24:24.840 --> 24:25.760
What's wrong?

24:28.280 --> 24:30.480
But she must be blessing me from heaven.

24:30.890 --> 24:31.370
Otherwise,

24:31.370 --> 24:33.230
I wouldn't have had such good luck

24:34.140 --> 24:35.340
to meet Jiang Cheng.

24:36.300 --> 24:38.230
Did you say goodbye to Jiang Cheng?

24:39.960 --> 24:40.520
I saw him,

24:41.700 --> 24:43.560
but I didn't mention I'm leaving.

24:46.130 --> 24:47.720
I'm not worth him missing me.

24:47.720 --> 24:49.370
Hey, what are you talking about?

24:49.370 --> 24:50.370
That's not true.

24:51.040 --> 24:53.440
Jiang Cheng will become better and better.

24:54.460 --> 24:55.660
I can't hold him back.

24:58.370 --> 25:02.060
Song, Lai San is unreliable.

25:03.210 --> 25:05.480
Something bad will happen sooner or later.

25:05.480 --> 25:06.650
Working with him

25:06.960 --> 25:08.810
is not as good
as working with Jiang Cheng.

25:08.810 --> 25:10.010
Keep my words in mind.

25:13.760 --> 25:15.820
Later, we waited at the agreed place.

25:17.050 --> 25:18.650
It was drizzling that night.

25:19.450 --> 25:21.980
Meng Ling didn't arrive
until around 11 or 12.

25:22.620 --> 25:24.410
Lai was already impatient from waiting,

25:24.410 --> 25:26.390
and he was in a bad mood
after drinking some alcohol.

25:26.390 --> 25:27.260
So when he saw Meng Ling,

25:27.260 --> 25:29.370
he didn't give her a good attitude at all.

25:29.370 --> 25:30.300
Get to the point.

25:30.520 --> 25:31.700
What exactly was the reason

25:31.700 --> 25:33.160
that made Lai San kill her?

25:34.000 --> 25:36.260
Meng Ling was too defensive against Lai.

25:36.410 --> 25:37.330
She was afraid of Lai's revenge,

25:37.330 --> 25:38.200
so she didn't bring

25:38.200 --> 25:39.730
the things he wanted at all.

25:39.890 --> 25:41.090
She was thinking of handing them over

25:41.090 --> 25:42.490
after she returned home.

25:42.610 --> 25:43.930
Lai got angry when he heard this,

25:43.930 --> 25:45.850
and told her not to
do things the hard way.

25:45.850 --> 25:47.610
Meng Ling stopped being afraid
when she heard this,

25:47.610 --> 25:48.480
and threatened Lai,

25:48.480 --> 25:50.330
saying she would give these things
to Boss He.

25:50.330 --> 25:51.650
Lai got even angrier when he heard this,

25:51.650 --> 25:53.000
and they started arguing.

25:53.000 --> 25:54.800
The argument was pretty normal,

25:54.820 --> 25:56.280
but for some reason, they suddenly

25:56.280 --> 25:57.610
mentioned Jiang Cheng.

25:57.610 --> 25:58.370
You also know

25:58.370 --> 26:00.240
Lai already hated Jiang Cheng.

26:00.240 --> 26:01.610
Lai said he would kill him,

26:01.610 --> 26:02.570
make him kneel in front of him,

26:02.570 --> 26:03.200
and kowtow to admit his mistake.

26:03.200 --> 26:04.000
When Meng Ling heard this,

26:04.000 --> 26:05.000
she got even angrier.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.000
Since Meng Ling was angry,

26:06.000 --> 26:07.170
she brought up

26:07.170 --> 26:08.260
Lai's past.

26:08.570 --> 26:09.410
What past?

26:17.810 --> 26:19.070
It was about a year ago.

26:21.170 --> 26:23.030
Lai's hand was broken by someone.

26:23.610 --> 26:25.650
He hates it when others mention it.

26:26.910 --> 26:28.860
Boss He wanted to help him get revenge.

26:28.860 --> 26:29.990
He wouldn't let him,

26:30.440 --> 26:32.400
saying nothing happened that day.

26:33.240 --> 26:34.040
But actually,

26:34.040 --> 26:35.640
a lot of people know about it.

26:36.470 --> 26:37.310
And then?

26:37.980 --> 26:41.040
Then Meng Ling said something
even Boss He doesn't dare

26:41.510 --> 26:42.420
to mention.

26:44.090 --> 26:45.130
Lai exploded.

26:46.880 --> 26:48.870
I knew people like you were unreliable!

26:47.390 --> 26:51.710
[July 24 00:16]

26:49.570 --> 26:51.330
If you don't hand over the stuff today,

26:51.330 --> 26:52.930
do you think you can walk away?

26:52.930 --> 26:54.530
Let me tell you this, Lai San.

26:54.610 --> 26:55.170
If I can't

26:55.170 --> 26:56.720
return to Honglian safely,

26:56.890 --> 26:58.220
you won't get the stuff.

26:58.280 --> 26:59.680
I'm being too nice to you.

27:00.170 --> 27:01.170
Save your breath.

27:01.700 --> 27:02.710
Where is it?

27:02.760 --> 27:04.040
I don't have it on me!

27:05.300 --> 27:07.260
Did you give it to Jiang Cheng?

27:07.760 --> 27:08.440
No.

27:09.130 --> 27:10.480
Just let me go,

27:10.720 --> 27:11.980
and I'll give it to you.

27:14.170 --> 27:15.410
Are you kidding me?

27:16.090 --> 27:17.570
Do you think hanging out with Jiang Cheng

27:17.570 --> 27:18.970
means he can protect you?

27:18.980 --> 27:20.550
He's nothing!

27:21.690 --> 27:22.690
See this?

27:23.720 --> 27:25.450
I'll shoot him sooner or later!

27:26.200 --> 27:27.650
Stay away from Cheng.

27:28.000 --> 27:29.280
You can't beat him.

27:30.040 --> 27:31.120
I can't beat him?

27:31.610 --> 27:33.570
If I can make him disappear for a year,

27:33.570 --> 27:35.570
I can make him disappear forever!

27:35.960 --> 27:37.560
Worry about yourself first.

27:37.940 --> 27:39.460
Don't get yourself killed first.

27:39.460 --> 27:40.240
What did you say?

27:40.240 --> 27:41.120
I said,

27:41.850 --> 27:43.650
Jiang Cheng is better than you.

27:43.850 --> 27:44.850
He's not like you,

27:44.960 --> 27:46.330
carrying a broken gun,

27:46.680 --> 27:47.940
pretending to be a man.

27:55.960 --> 27:56.810
That's it.

27:58.570 --> 27:59.410
Where were you then?

27:59.410 --> 28:00.370
What were you doing?

28:00.370 --> 28:02.200
I was in the car.

28:02.200 --> 28:03.720
It was cold. I...

28:03.720 --> 28:05.610
I had no idea what happened.

28:06.210 --> 28:08.100
I was terrified.

28:08.660 --> 28:09.720
What about Lai San?

28:11.570 --> 28:13.030
After he killed Meng Ling,

28:13.810 --> 28:14.930
he was stunned too.

28:15.650 --> 28:17.380
It took him a long time to react.

28:18.490 --> 28:19.330
I guess

28:19.810 --> 28:22.140
he also felt things
had gotten out of hand.

28:23.060 --> 28:25.340
After about five or six minutes,

28:26.140 --> 28:27.400
he came back to the car.

28:46.040 --> 28:46.810
You saw.

28:48.350 --> 28:49.730
I didn't see anything, Lai.

28:49.730 --> 28:50.760
I saw nothing.

28:50.760 --> 28:51.570
You have to believe me.

28:51.570 --> 28:53.170
I will never betray you, Lai!

28:53.480 --> 28:54.200
Lai,

28:54.520 --> 28:56.380
I can help you get rid of Meng Ling!

28:56.760 --> 28:57.650
Lai.

28:57.810 --> 28:58.520
Lai,

28:58.930 --> 29:01.680
only I can help you now!

29:01.680 --> 29:04.480
Don't kill me, don't kill me.

29:04.570 --> 29:06.720
I'm begging you, don't kill me.

29:11.130 --> 29:12.660
I know where your mother is.

29:15.520 --> 29:16.650
Don't play tricks on me.

29:16.650 --> 29:17.570
I won't.

29:17.570 --> 29:19.480
I won't, Lai.

29:31.490 --> 29:33.150
He asked me to withdraw money,

29:33.480 --> 29:35.940
so he could pack up
and run away immediately.

29:36.570 --> 29:39.460
I was afraid
someone passing by would see it,

29:40.370 --> 29:42.200
so I reminded him

29:44.040 --> 29:46.850
to at least hide the body first.

29:48.240 --> 29:49.370
You are quite smart.

29:49.760 --> 29:50.470
But you didn't expect

29:50.470 --> 29:52.470
the body to be found so soon, did you?

29:58.850 --> 30:01.570
That day,
precisely because of Huang Song's help,

30:01.570 --> 30:03.770
Lai Zhengtian thought he could get away

30:04.490 --> 30:06.000
after killing and dumping the body

30:06.000 --> 30:07.650
and even gave up fleeing.

30:08.350 --> 30:09.330
So arrogant.

30:09.810 --> 30:11.870
No wonder in the interrogation room,

30:11.930 --> 30:14.590
he acted like he had
absolutely nothing to lose.

30:15.130 --> 30:16.440
He really thought the police

30:16.440 --> 30:18.770
would never get the evidence to catch him.

30:18.890 --> 30:19.720
Now,

30:19.720 --> 30:21.410
we have the evidence.

30:21.930 --> 30:23.790
I'm not worried he won't confess.

30:23.930 --> 30:25.790
Did he say anything about the gun?

30:25.810 --> 30:27.520
He didn't know its origin either.

30:27.520 --> 30:28.520
Where is the gun?

30:28.610 --> 30:30.470
He said only Lai Zhengtian knows.

30:30.610 --> 30:33.090
The gun isn't in
any of Lai Zhengtian's hideouts.

30:33.090 --> 30:35.410
We can't be sure
if he threw it in the river or not.

30:35.410 --> 30:38.000
Now, it depends on his attitude
for confessing

30:38.000 --> 30:40.730
and whether he wants to
behave well for leniency.

30:41.410 --> 30:42.010
It's hard.

30:42.480 --> 30:43.540
Indeed, it's hard.

30:44.170 --> 30:45.330
Lai Zhengtian is guilty of

30:45.330 --> 30:47.150
intentional homicide,
organizing prostitution,

30:47.150 --> 30:48.840
and provoking trouble.

30:49.440 --> 30:50.890
He'll be punished for multiple crimes.

30:50.890 --> 30:51.610
I guess

30:52.040 --> 30:53.970
he understands better than anyone

30:54.040 --> 30:56.130
that even if he confesses
to the gun's origin,

30:56.130 --> 30:57.570
it won't bring him any good results.

30:57.570 --> 30:58.340
And

30:58.770 --> 31:00.090
if people outside found out

31:00.090 --> 31:01.440
he snitched,

31:01.510 --> 31:02.960
the ensuing revenge

31:03.810 --> 31:05.480
would be more fatal than his sentence.

31:05.480 --> 31:06.480
Professor Jiang,

31:07.000 --> 31:08.730
do you have any other opinions?

31:12.310 --> 31:14.710
We're still missing one piece of evidence.

31:14.750 --> 31:17.080
We still don't know
what dirt Meng Ling had

31:17.440 --> 31:18.650
on Lai Zhengtian.

31:19.380 --> 31:20.520
I asked Huang Song about this,

31:20.520 --> 31:21.980
but he didn't know either.

31:22.560 --> 31:23.930
No matter who knows,

31:23.950 --> 31:25.410
is the evidence we have now

31:25.520 --> 31:26.920
enough to close the case?

31:28.040 --> 31:29.000
Tomorrow morning,

31:29.000 --> 31:30.680
I will apply for a search warrant

31:30.680 --> 31:32.240
and go to Meng Ling's place again.

31:32.240 --> 31:33.680
Maybe we can find new clues.

31:33.680 --> 31:34.610
I'll go with you.

31:34.760 --> 31:35.580
Huang Song confessed

31:35.580 --> 31:36.280
he got Meng Ling's suitcase

31:36.280 --> 31:37.520
back from the driver.

31:37.680 --> 31:38.760
He kept it with him

31:38.930 --> 31:40.130
and hasn't dealt with it.

31:40.130 --> 31:40.680
Okay.

31:41.520 --> 31:42.050
Alright.

31:42.410 --> 31:43.740
Let's call it a day here.

31:44.570 --> 31:46.440
Everyone, go back and get some rest.

31:46.440 --> 31:47.610
Tomorrow,

31:47.610 --> 31:49.940
after Zhou Jin's search results come out,

31:50.040 --> 31:52.040
we will continue to sort things out.

31:52.560 --> 31:53.230
Dismissed.

31:53.280 --> 31:54.130
-Yes.
-Yes.

31:56.760 --> 31:59.720
You guys better lock in tomorrow.

32:00.410 --> 32:01.870
A senior leader is coming.

32:03.520 --> 32:06.000
The former head
of the 8.17 Case's task force,

32:06.000 --> 32:06.960
Yao Weihai.

32:07.810 --> 32:10.420
He is here to assist us
in our future work.

32:11.040 --> 32:13.130
Lai Zhengtian's gun is hard to trace,

32:13.440 --> 32:14.770
but if we don't trace it,

32:15.090 --> 32:16.890
it will become a cold case again.

32:56.570 --> 32:57.770
Is there a problem?

33:03.090 --> 33:04.090
You must be tired.

33:07.240 --> 33:08.680
If you have any ideas,

33:08.940 --> 33:10.600
we can discuss them together.

33:15.610 --> 33:17.000
I want to think alone.

33:18.090 --> 33:19.550
You go back to sleep first.

33:40.720 --> 33:41.370
Okay.

33:46.680 --> 33:47.440
Zhou Jin.

34:07.660 --> 34:08.550
Good night.

35:12.160 --> 35:13.560
Boss He thought highly of Jiang Cheng

35:13.560 --> 35:15.370
as soon as he joined the company.

35:16.290 --> 35:17.370
Phoenix Fire

35:17.370 --> 35:20.160
is now fully managed by Jiang Cheng.

35:20.160 --> 35:21.170
Meng Ling told me

35:21.200 --> 35:23.060
Cheng was a different kind of man.

35:25.560 --> 35:26.770
We're still missing a piece
of physical evidence.

35:26.770 --> 35:28.640
We still don't know
what dirt Meng Ling had

35:28.640 --> 35:29.850
on Lai Zhengtian.

36:42.730 --> 36:43.480
I had

36:45.160 --> 36:46.690
a boyfriend

36:46.690 --> 36:47.810
for many years.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.210
His name is Jiang Cheng, right?

37:14.330 --> 37:15.260
If you can let go,

37:15.430 --> 37:16.230
then I can too.

37:40.390 --> 37:41.390
Professor Jiang!

37:42.350 --> 37:43.350
Professor Jiang.

37:43.570 --> 37:43.970
Hello.

37:44.040 --> 37:44.560
Hello,

37:45.160 --> 37:45.810
Yang.

37:45.810 --> 37:47.250
I'm the technical investigator,

37:47.250 --> 37:47.800
Bai Yang.

37:48.930 --> 37:49.890
Sorry for disturbing your rest.

37:49.890 --> 37:50.730
No, not at all.

37:51.290 --> 37:53.350
I'd like to see Huang Song's
interrogation video.

37:53.350 --> 37:54.080
Is that okay?

37:55.210 --> 37:56.350
Yes, of course.

37:56.490 --> 37:58.270
Chief Tan gave instructions earlier

37:58.270 --> 38:01.000
that if you have any requests
regarding the case,

38:01.480 --> 38:02.370
as long as it's not against the rules,

38:02.370 --> 38:03.960
we should give you the green light.

38:03.960 --> 38:04.600
Thank you.

38:04.890 --> 38:05.690
No problem.

38:05.690 --> 38:06.810
We're colleagues, no need to be polite.

38:06.810 --> 38:07.620
Besides,

38:08.050 --> 38:09.710
you're the CIB's son-in-law.

38:12.370 --> 38:14.080
Why do you suddenly want to
watch this video?

38:14.080 --> 38:15.720
Is there anything suspicious?

38:15.720 --> 38:17.450
There are some unusual points.

38:19.680 --> 38:20.940
But she wasn't honest.

38:21.410 --> 38:22.890
She had something on Lai.

38:24.600 --> 38:25.000
Lai said

38:25.000 --> 38:26.210
she was a hot potato.

38:27.040 --> 38:28.840
She needed to be dealt with ASAP.

38:28.850 --> 38:30.080
What did she have on him?

38:30.080 --> 38:30.810
I don't know.

38:31.330 --> 38:33.560
Does dealing with her ASAP
mean killing her?

38:33.560 --> 38:35.620
We didn't intend to kill her at first.

38:41.280 --> 38:44.310
I was afraid someone passing by would see.

38:45.220 --> 38:47.010
So I reminded him

38:48.770 --> 38:51.760
to at least hide the body first.

38:52.370 --> 38:53.500
You're quite smart.

38:53.730 --> 38:54.250
But you didn't expect

38:54.250 --> 38:56.450
the body to be found so quickly, did you?

38:57.690 --> 38:58.520
How is it?

38:58.930 --> 38:59.730
Play it again.

39:00.230 --> 39:00.980
At 2x speed.

39:03.370 --> 39:03.890
Okay.

39:06.880 --> 39:09.170
What's the relationship between Meng Ling
and Lai Zhengtian?

39:09.170 --> 39:10.560
Meng Ling was one of Lai's girls.

39:10.560 --> 39:11.960
She was the most popular among the guests.

39:11.960 --> 39:13.000
But she wasn't honest.

39:13.000 --> 39:14.400
She had something on Lai.

39:14.600 --> 39:15.860
Lai said she’s a hot potato.

39:15.860 --> 39:17.340
She needed to be dealt with ASAP.

39:17.340 --> 39:18.670
What did she have on him?

39:19.710 --> 39:20.890
Does dealing with her ASAP
mean killing her?

39:20.890 --> 39:21.830
We didn't intend to kill her at first

39:21.830 --> 39:22.500
because...

39:22.810 --> 39:23.730
Jiang Cheng came back.

39:23.730 --> 39:24.790
Lai was afraid of him.

39:24.790 --> 39:27.390
This Lai San
doesn't dare to touch Jiang Cheng.

39:28.080 --> 39:29.520
Lai has been having bad luck.

39:29.520 --> 39:30.100
He was afraid
that after Jiang Cheng's return,

39:30.100 --> 39:31.120
he wouldn't be able to keep his position.

39:31.120 --> 39:31.690
So,

39:31.810 --> 39:33.120
he hasn't dared to
make a single mistake recently.

39:33.120 --> 39:34.040
Would touching Meng Ling
be considered a mistake?

39:34.040 --> 39:35.080
How could it not be?

39:35.080 --> 39:35.930
Meng Ling used to be with Jiang Cheng.

39:35.930 --> 39:36.730
If Lai really touched her,

39:36.730 --> 39:37.600
Jiang Cheng would end him.

39:37.600 --> 39:38.160
Explain clearly.

39:38.160 --> 39:38.640
She was with Jiang Cheng.

39:38.640 --> 39:39.330
In what way?

39:40.040 --> 39:41.440
Just... that kind of way.

39:41.560 --> 39:42.160
As lovers.

39:42.620 --> 39:43.060
Go on.

39:44.600 --> 39:45.080
Lai said

39:45.290 --> 39:46.410
Jiang Cheng used to be a cop.

39:46.410 --> 39:47.600
If Jiang Cheng
really wanted to mess with him,

39:47.600 --> 39:48.480
he might not be able to handle it.

39:48.480 --> 39:49.930
You all know Jiang Cheng used to be a cop?

39:49.930 --> 39:50.520
Yes.

39:50.890 --> 39:52.830
I heard he was dismissed
for violating discipline.

39:52.830 --> 39:54.290
Later he followed Boss He...

39:54.290 --> 39:55.380
and went into business.

39:55.380 --> 39:56.240
What business?

39:56.810 --> 39:58.610
Making a gangster sound so nice.

39:58.910 --> 39:59.540
A cop?

40:00.500 --> 40:01.700
Don't dirty our name.

40:09.130 --> 40:10.130
Professor Jiang.

40:11.040 --> 40:12.040
Professor Jiang.

40:17.740 --> 40:18.770
Did you see it?

40:19.370 --> 40:20.990
See... See what?

40:21.730 --> 40:22.930
In this part just now,

40:23.290 --> 40:26.220
pay attention to the change
in Huang Song's posture.

40:28.000 --> 40:28.930
In your opinion,

40:29.250 --> 40:30.850
what state is he in right now?

40:32.110 --> 40:32.860
He...

40:33.890 --> 40:35.490
is very afraid of the police.

40:36.450 --> 40:37.640
Ah, that's normal.

40:37.670 --> 40:39.800
He's a gangster

40:40.120 --> 40:42.150
and more mature than students his age,

40:42.150 --> 40:42.800
but

40:43.080 --> 40:45.210
no matter how mature, he's still a kid.

40:45.560 --> 40:46.690
Quite the opposite.

40:47.330 --> 40:48.260
He's not afraid.

40:49.960 --> 40:51.490
He's not curling up in fear.

40:51.850 --> 40:53.310
It's a defensive posture.

40:54.740 --> 40:57.540
When he heard remarks
detrimental to Jiang Cheng,

40:58.080 --> 40:59.330
his body tensed,

40:59.480 --> 41:01.680
and his eyes quickly showed hostility.

41:01.770 --> 41:02.900
This state

41:03.250 --> 41:05.050
lasted less than a second or two,

41:05.440 --> 41:07.250
but this is his most genuine

41:07.350 --> 41:08.550
reflexive reaction.

41:09.480 --> 41:10.410
Extreme anger.

41:13.290 --> 41:14.120
And here.

41:17.920 --> 41:20.800
I was afraid someone passing by would see,

41:21.860 --> 41:23.460
so I reminded him

41:24.890 --> 41:28.330
to at least hide the body first.

41:38.280 --> 41:39.780
In crimes committed by groups

41:39.780 --> 41:40.850
of two or more people,

41:40.850 --> 41:42.580
usually the one with more power

41:42.580 --> 41:44.910
or a stronger desire for power and control

41:44.930 --> 41:46.530
is in the dominant position,

41:46.640 --> 41:48.570
while the others are subordinate.

41:49.480 --> 41:49.960
Then

41:50.410 --> 41:52.160
the decision-maker should be

41:52.210 --> 41:53.070
Lai Zhengtian.

41:53.730 --> 41:54.120
Yes.

41:55.440 --> 41:57.000
Whether in age,

41:57.040 --> 41:57.640
personality,

41:57.640 --> 41:58.500
social status,

41:59.100 --> 41:59.910
Lai Zhengtian

41:59.980 --> 42:02.120
is far superior to Huang Song
in all aspects.

42:02.120 --> 42:04.780
And given Huang Song's
premature experiences,

42:04.900 --> 42:06.180
he is in a state of absolute obedience

42:06.180 --> 42:07.650
to Lai Zhengtian.

42:08.850 --> 42:10.050
When the dominant one

42:10.250 --> 42:12.360
is more inclined to flee quickly,

42:12.930 --> 42:13.850
and the subordinate

42:13.850 --> 42:15.080
can calm down first,

42:16.040 --> 42:17.520
propose a body disposal plan,

42:17.520 --> 42:19.560
and take the lead
in covering up the crime,

42:19.560 --> 42:21.000
this is a typical conflict
between personality

42:21.000 --> 42:22.670
and criminal behavior.

42:25.040 --> 42:26.370
Is it possible

42:26.400 --> 42:28.440
for the accomplice to strategize

42:28.560 --> 42:29.440
and take over?

42:31.000 --> 42:31.780
Of course.

42:32.680 --> 42:33.740
But this situation

42:33.940 --> 42:35.320
stems more from the accomplice's worship

42:35.320 --> 42:36.630
of the principal criminal

42:36.630 --> 42:38.030
or long-term obedience.

42:38.930 --> 42:39.790
In other words,

42:40.160 --> 42:42.040
they would take the initiative
to clean up the crime scene

42:42.040 --> 42:44.370
out of an absolute desire to protect them,

42:44.440 --> 42:46.170
and may even cover up the crime.

42:47.080 --> 42:48.140
But think about it.

42:49.080 --> 42:51.770
If Huang Song really wanted to
protect Lai Zhengtian,

42:51.770 --> 42:53.040
why would he so easily

42:53.500 --> 42:55.860
reveal Lai Zhengtian's

42:55.890 --> 42:57.220
entire murder process?

42:58.560 --> 43:00.090
Isn't this contradictory?

43:01.730 --> 43:04.250
Huang Song's description of the murder
and body disposal process

43:04.250 --> 43:05.180
is not credible.

43:06.000 --> 43:07.120
Indeed.
